#: ../../source/controllers/stopwatch.rst:49
#: ../../source/controllers/stopwatch.rst:95 6271fe804e994251a187e0076e8125ea
msgid ""
"This example demonstrates audio recording and playback. Press **BtnA** to"
" start a 5-second recording (countdown shown on screen). Press **BtnB** "
"to play back the recorded file when not recording. The UI shows **Idle**,"
" **Recording...**, or **Playing...** status."
msgstr ""
"此示例演示录音与播放。按 **BtnA** 开始录制 5 秒（屏幕显示倒计时）。未在录制时按 **BtnB** "
"播放已录制的文件。界面显示 **Idle**、**Recording...** 或 **Playing...** 状态。"

